{"tid":1894474,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"杜克大學教授警告要管制性愛機械人：危害人們的道德與心理","createTime":"2020-02-24T02:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T13:12:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"efcdb86b7863763543b732bc09be4db43c9ae3ba","tid":1894474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"因為各種組織和單位都羞於調查性愛機械人，讓這樣的科技較不易受到監督，有意者可能會透過性愛機械人收集到人類更多隱密的資訊。以下是中央社全文報導：<br />\n<img src=\"https://sw.cool3c.com/user/6/2020/fc5d1d4f-ada2-4de3-953d-16b81ae379f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsw.cool3c.com%2Fuser%2F6%2F2020%2Ffc5d1d4f-ada2-4de3-953d-16b81ae379f7.jpg&h=bf195c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：人類滅亡計畫之一睹中國性愛機器人生產流程<br />\n<br />\n研究人員警告，具備人工智慧（AI）的性愛機械人問世後，對個人和社會構成愈來愈多心理與道德威脅。科學家呼籲，應採取行動管制使用這類機器人。英國廣播公司（BBC）報導，研究人員指出，由於各機構羞於調查，讓這種科技不受監督。<br />\n<br />\n美國杜克大學（Duke University）的韓德倫博士（Christine Hendren）在美國科學促進會（AAAS）年會告訴BBC，性愛機械人構成的「風險很高」。她說，為了營造強暴情境，有些機械人被設計來抵抗人類。還有一些機械人具備孩童外觀，<span style=\"color: red;\">一名自認有戀童癖的日本開發人士聲稱，這類機械人能預防他去傷害真正的孩童。</span><br />\n<br />\n但韓德倫質疑：「難道那不會正常化應該被根除的行為，反而讓人有機會練習這些行為嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n目前網路上已有一些性愛機器人的廣告。以美國公司Realbotix的Harmony機器人為例，這款機器人大小如同真人，可以眨眼、移動眼球和脖子，還能模仿真人說話的樣子動唇。一具Harmony要價8000至1萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n據公司創辦人兼執行長麥穆倫（Matt McMullen）解釋，Harmony具備人工智慧，能跟「她」的擁有者發展關係。麥穆倫說：「她會記得有關你的事、你的好惡和經歷。」<br />\n<br />\n但英國列斯特（Leicester）德蒙福大學（De Montfort University）機器人暨AI道德與文化教授李察遜（Kathleen Richardson）希望立法禁止這類行銷。李察遜說：「這些公司表達的是『你沒朋友嗎？缺人生伴侶嗎？別擔心，我們能幫你製造機器人女友。』（但）跟女友的關係是建立在親密、愛慕和互助之上，機器無法複製這類事情。」"},{"pid":"a4397a0c66374bb238020b154e44cddeb36d9acb","tid":1894474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/151762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F151762&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=c1469f6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/151762</a>"},{"pid":"89d566cec6ffb5a0beb706a68c813c8ba5bf6c42","tid":1894474,"uid":42340,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n啲死鬼佬連毒撚打個飛機都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b682dc61fcf38f2951ce7212f6d0f8d1f42face0","tid":1894474,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"［黃色新聞圈］香港人 肯 撐 良 心 傳 媒 未，肯唔好扼殺佢地未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b0dc5f03026e0b1c2aa616e42b05061427a94dc","tid":1894474,"uid":80243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:58:31.000Z","msg":"有得揀會做可憐賓周咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd94c487fc9de67b75d970297a6668f3419fa4b","tid":1894474,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"那有女你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c4b906b00585b64da075277d7c6960759660d9","tid":1894474,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"到時人人都可以有個機械人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲臭雞仲會唔會吊高黎賣厄鳩啲男仔死追爛追"},{"pid":"8a1e23501aa08dca43cd930930581ba93e224cb3","tid":1894474,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"